# directive-at-eof

## Input

```
#version 1.0
```

## CST

```
SOURCE_FILE@0..12
  DIRECTIVE@0..12
    SHARP@0..1 "#"
    WORD@1..8 "version"
    LINE_STRING@8..12
      STRING@8..12 " 1.0"
```

## AST

```
SourceFile {
    shebang: none,
    items: [
        Directive {
            sharp: SHARP@0..1 "#",
            name: WORD@1..8 "version",
            args: LineString {
                string: STRING@8..12 " 1.0",
            },
        },
    ],
}
```

